item.title: Error with making ancients turn on with a prayer at an alter
item.dc:creator: @lothy Lothy
item.description:
@lothy wrote:

[quote=“Runey, post:1, topic:54224”]I keep getting this

client.java:15614:cannot find symbol symbol:variable objectID location:class client if (objectID == 6552 && emotes == 0 || emotes == 1)[/quote]
Are you doing that inside the objectClick void or whatever it’s called? Because the variable objectID isn’t public - it doesn’t exist outside of any of the methods.
that, and if(objectID == ####) { is sufficient - you don’t need the emote stuff there.
